        'card.blueteam.title': 'Blue Team / SOC',
        'card.blueteam.desc': 'Persistent algorithmic scrutiny tracking digital perimeters terminating unacknowledged malicious manifestations synchronously ensuring complete localized pacification.',
        'card.blueteam.li1': '24/7 SIEM Observation',
        'card.blueteam.li2': 'Active Threat Tracking',
        'card.blueteam.li3': 'Immediate IR Containment',
        'card.blueteam.li4': 'Malware Deconstruction',
        'card.audit.title': 'Audit & Governance',
        'card.audit.desc': 'Forging uncompromising legislative documentation perfectly fulfilling necessary global corporative certification parameters strictly mandating compliance.',
        'card.audit.li1': 'ISO Implementation',
        'card.audit.li2': 'Procedural Regulation',
        'card.audit.li3': 'Human Cognitive Defense',
        'card.audit.li4': 'Monetary Risk Analytics',
        'whyus.tag': '// VALIDATION',
        'whyus.heading': 'Architectural Superiors',
                'whyus.c1.title': 'Absolute Defense',
        'whyus.c1.desc': 'Our approach neutralizes even zero-day vulnerabilities deep within your network core. We provide an uncompromising corporate shield against both external threats and internal architectural breaches, ensuring 24/7 continuous protection.',
        'whyus.c2.title': 'Rapid Incident Response',
        'whyus.c2.desc': 'Powered by AI-driven behavioral analytics rather than static rules, our proactive system identifies and destroys anomalies within milliseconds. By shutting down lateral movement capabilities, we prevent crises instantly with zero data loss.',
        'whyus.c3.title': 'Cryptographic Privacy (NDA)',
        'whyus.c3.desc': 'Our protection adheres to Military-Grade AES-256 encryption standards. Your strategic plans, client databases, and account secrets are flawlessly isolated from competitors and third-party services, secured under strict legal obligations.',
        'whyus.c4.title': 'Continuous SOC Monitoring',
        'whyus.c4.desc': 'Billions of data transactions are continuously filtered by our Security Operations Center (SOC). We hunt down dormant, highly sophisticated APT malware before it executes, neutralizing threats in real-time on our visual dashboards.',
        'whyus.c5.title': 'Analytical Reports',
        'whyus.c5.desc': 'Tailored specifically for C-Level executives, our executive summaries translate complex technical risk vectors into clear business impacts. We deliver transparent ROI matrices to prove exactly how your security budget prevents catastrophic losses.',
        'cta.heading': 'Initiate Architectural Diagnostics?',
        'cta.desc': 'First phase analytical evaluation inherently remains complimentary. Secure existing assets comprehensively today instantly.',
        'cta.btn': '// INITIATE_CONTACT',
